extends layout

block pageTitle
  title About Hedge Wears

block metaDesc
  meta(name='description' content='Hedge Wears was built to put African fashion on the global stage. Refined classics with cultural weight and contemporary relevance.')

block content

  //- ─── HERO ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.about-hero.hero--image.section(style='background-image: url("https://hedgewears.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/10/ctaimage.webp")')
    .hero-overlay
    .container
      .about-hero-inner
        span.section-eyebrow Our story
        h1.about-hero-title About Hedge Wears
        p.about-hero-sub African creativity on the global stage. Refined classics with cultural weight and contemporary relevance.

  //- ─── MISSION ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.mission.section.section--dark
    .container
      .mission-inner
        .mission-statement
          span.section-eyebrow Our mission
          blockquote.mission-quote
            | &ldquo;We built Hedge Wears to put African fashion on the global stage.&rdquo;
        .mission-body
          p We started Hedge Wears from a conviction that the African fashion industry &mdash; one of the most creative, vibrant, and culturally rich in the world &mdash; deserved better infrastructure. Local designers were building incredible things. Buyers were looking for them. The two were just not meeting.
          p Hedge Wears is the bridge. A platform where sellers can list their products, run their business, and get paid without complexity &mdash; and where shoppers can discover fashion that carries real cultural weight. Every purchase earns HedgeCoin, turning loyalty into real savings.
          p Today, Hedge Wears connects thousands of shoppers with hundreds of brands across Africa. New sellers and products join every day, and we are just getting started.

  //- ─── VALUES ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.values.section
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow What we believe
        h2.section-title Our values

      .values-grid
        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            svg.value-icon(width='28' height='28' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M12 2C8.13 2 5 5.13 5 9c0 5.25 7 13 7 13s7-7.75 7-13c0-3.87-3.13-7-7-7z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
              circle(cx='12' cy='9' r='2.5' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8')
          h3.value-title Local First
          p.value-desc We champion African designers and fashion entrepreneurs. Hedge Wears is a platform built to amplify local talent, not displace it. Every feature we ship is designed to help local businesses grow.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            svg.value-icon(width='28' height='28' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M1 12s4-8 11-8 11 8 11 8-4 8-11 8-11-8-11-8z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
              circle(cx='12' cy='12' r='3' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8')
          h3.value-title Transparency
          p.value-desc Pricing is clear. HedgeCoin is straightforward. No hidden fees, no confusing terms. What you see is what you get &mdash; on every product page and at every checkout.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            svg.value-icon(width='28' height='28' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              circle(cx='12' cy='12' r='9' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8')
              path(d='M12 7v1m0 8v1M9.5 9.5C9.5 8.67 10.67 8 12 8s2.5.67 2.5 1.5S13.33 11 12 11s-2.5.83-2.5 1.5S10.67 15 12 15s2.5-.67 2.5-1.5' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round')
          h3.value-title Rewarding Loyalty
          p.value-desc Shopping here benefits you every time. The HedgeCoin reward system exists to give back to the people who keep the platform alive: our customers. HGC earned never expires while your account is active.

        .value-card
          .value-icon-wrap
            svg.value-icon(width='28' height='28' viewBox='0 0 24 24' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' aria-hidden='true')
              path(d='M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z' stroke='currentColor' stroke-width='1.8' stroke-linecap='round' stroke-linejoin='round')
          h3.value-title Simple by Design
          p.value-desc Every feature we ship has to earn its place. If it doesn&rsquo;t make shopping or selling meaningfully easier, we cut it. Complexity is a bug, not a feature.

  //- ─── TEAM ──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.team.section.section--muted
    .container
      .section-header
        span.section-eyebrow The people
        h2.section-title Behind Hedge Wears
        p.section-subtitle A small team of designers, engineers, and fashion enthusiasts working to build something lasting.

      .team-grid
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder(aria-hidden='true')
            span.team-avatar-initials F
          .team-info
            span.team-name Founder &amp; CEO
            span.team-role Building the vision
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder(aria-hidden='true')
            span.team-avatar-initials P
          .team-info
            span.team-name Head of Product
            span.team-role Designing the experience
        .team-card.team-card--placeholder
          .team-avatar-placeholder(aria-hidden='true')
            span.team-avatar-initials D
          .team-info
            span.team-name Head of Design
            span.team-role Shaping the aesthetic

  //- ─── STATS ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.stats-bar.section
    .container
      .stats-grid
        .stat-item
          span.stat-number 500+
          span.stat-label Brands
        .stat-divider
        .stat-item
          span.stat-number 50,000+
          span.stat-label Customers
        .stat-divider
        .stat-item
          span.stat-number 10,000+
          span.stat-label Products

  //- ─── JOIN CTA ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
  section.cta-banner.section
    .container
      .cta-banner-inner
        h2.cta-banner-title Join us
        p.cta-banner-subtitle Be part of the platform putting African fashion on the global stage.
        .cta-banner-actions
          a.btn.btn-white.btn-lg(href=webShopUrl target='_blank' rel='noopener') Start Shopping
          a.btn.btn-outline-white.btn-lg(href='/contact') Get in Touch
